reviews.review_text:
Best Sounding Version Here Some hiss at the top end, but full and robust in the bottom.

Thanks archive.
Pig Pen's last show in circulation nice! everything is right here. this particular mix sounds great.  more up front and "hot"-- I love it.    Speed

Best of Europe Picking the best of the E'72 is really splitting hairs, but I think this is the one!
It is all so good. The Truckin> Other One> Dew> Other One> Sing Me and the jams between puts this one over the top (sorry to 5/4 and 5/11).
